"```sql\nSELECT Player.player_name, AVG(Player_Attributes.finishing) AS average_finishing\nFROM Player\nINNER JOIN Player_Attributes ON Player.player_api_id = Player_Attributes.player_api_id\nWHERE Player.height = (SELECT MAX(height) FROM Player) OR Player.height = (SELECT MIN(height) FROM Player)\nGROUP BY Player.player_name\nORDER BY average_finishing DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```"